2018-06-10T22:15:00.000Z,Lfek7Kcq16g,Just Cause 4 - Official Reveal Trailer | E3 2018,"Unification or Death (Serbian: Уједињење или смрт / Ujedinjenje ili smrt), popularly known as the Black Hand (Црна рука / Crna ruka), was a secret military society formed on 9 May 1911 by officers in the Army of the Kingdom of Serbia, originating in the conspiracy group that assassinated the Serbian royal couple (1903), led by captain Dragutin Dimitrijević ""Apis"".

It was formed with the aim of uniting all of the territories with a South Slavic majority not ruled by either Serbia or Montenegro. Its inspiration was primarily the unification of Italy in 1859–70, but also that of Germany in 1871.[1][2] Through its connections to the June 1914 assassination of Archduke Franz Ferdinand in Sarajevo, which was committed by the members of youth movement Young Bosnia, the Black Hand is often viewed as having contributed to the start of World War I by precipitating the July Crisis of 1914, which eventually led to Austria-Hungary's invasion of the Kingdom of Serbia.[3]",2018-06-13T10:02:44.000Z,0

2018-06-10T22:15:00.000Z,Lfek7Kcq16g,Just Cause 4 - Official Reveal Trailer | E3 2018,"So rico has the same voice and outfit from JC2, and the map is similar. It's almost like they just forgot about just cause 3, even though it's a continuation of the Bavarium Sea Heist.
Anyway, this looks like the best just cause game yet. Good voice acting, great graphics, and new things such as natural disasters (blizzards, sandstorms, tornadoes, etc.)

I also love the new enemies, like the ones with shields and others with drones. It really does make it feel like they are powerful and capable of anything. In just cause 3, the only thing that separated enemies were their armor and resistance, and throw in a couple of snipers and rocket launchers.
Just Cause 3 was way to easy to beat. You were too strong and enemies were too weak. I hope this game is harder than the previous one. This game had better have a decent story as well.
Just Cause 3s story was somewhat mediocre, but wasn't great. I seriously hope this games story can at least beat just cause 2s, which the 3rd one couldn't do.

Overall, this game looks great and I can't wait to own it. Just Cause 3 got boring after a while because things got repetitive too fast. I hope this game doesn't do the same. I personally think this was the best e3 yet, but I may be wrong.
How do you preorder it on steam?",2018-06-11T07:09:14.000Z,0
